161
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:03,793
Was it really you?

162
00:09:04,377 --> 00:09:06,504
Yes, it was all me.

163
00:09:07,171 --> 00:09:08,464
And you were there, too.

164
00:09:22,937 --> 00:09:24,105
Tasty Hotdogs

165
00:09:24,188 --> 00:09:26,399
-[customer grunts]
-[blasting]

166
