170
00:09:58,723 --> 00:10:00,683
[Pil] The serial arsonist's next target
is Next Officetel.

171
00:10:00,766 --> 00:10:01,851
We require immediate assistance.

172
00:10:03,394 --> 00:10:04,395
[sighs]

173
